 Boxing Championships, Khelif has spoken out.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a defiant response\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"her disqualification\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's World Boxing Championships\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Boxing Association (IBA) disqualified Khelif after she failed a gender eligibility test, which the IBA insists was not related to testosterone levels but rather other competitive advantages.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.925613574587067e-30, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999930480508461, \"rank\": 6.935855033644124e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999930480508461, \"rank\": 6.935855033644124e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"a gender eligibility test\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1966}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone levels\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"other competitive advantages\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the IBA's confidentiality on the specifics of the test, President Umar Kremlev claimed that the tests indicated XY chromosomes, leading to Khelif's exclusion.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999930480508461, \"rank\": 6.935855033644124e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"score\": 0.9999999915812623, \"rank\": 8.418844639279672e-09, \"text\": \"Umar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the specifics\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's exclusion\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on her challenging journey, Khelif - whose career record is 42 wins in 51 fights with nine losses - said: \\\"The year 2023 was very difficult for me after a great year... \\\"It was a hard blow for me but I came back stronger to show my strength and my determination and show the whole world what a brave woman Imane Khelif is.\\\"\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her challenging journey\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"whose career record\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"42 wins\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"51 fights\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"nine losses\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"The year\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"a great year\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"a hard blow\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"my strength\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"my determination\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"what a brave woman\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on Canal Algerie, she revealed: \\\"I come from a conservative region and family.\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Canal Algerie\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"a conservative region\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing was a sport dedicated only to men.\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are obstacles that I encountered when I started.\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"obstacles\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I happened to sell bread in the street, I collected dishes and other objects to earn money and to be able to move around because I came from a very poor family.\\\"\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bread\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"dishes\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"other objects\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"a very poor family\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her passion for boxing ignited instantly upon entering the ring, and with unwavering resolve, she transitioned from her humble beginnings in a small village to the bustling city life and ultimately the capital.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her passion\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"unwavering resolve\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"her humble beginnings\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3065}, {\"ngram\": \"a small village\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"the bustling city life\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"ultimately the capital\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif regards her ascent as an \\\"impressive story\\\" and takes immense pride in her accomplishments.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"her ascent\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"impressive story\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"immense pride\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"her accomplishments\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on her unexpected rise in the boxing world, she said: \\\"It was pure chance, I never imagined one day that I would become a boxer and that I would become world champion.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her unexpected rise\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxing world\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"pure chance\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"a boxer\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always loved football and I played it in my little village.\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"my little village\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My father always preferred football to boxing.\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My father\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was very good at sports in my school and my teacher encouraged me to become a boxer since I had good physical qualities and he was right.\\\"\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"my school\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3578}, {\"ngram\": \"my teacher\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"a boxer\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3625}, {\"ngram\": \"good physical qualities\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has her eyes set on Olympic glory, advancing to the women's welterweight quarterfinals this Saturday where she faces Hungary's Anna Luca Hamori.\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3806, \"end\": 3813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9987282927924355, \"rank\": 0.0012555431560629096, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 3816, \"end\": 3820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9994318130911094, \"rank\": 0.0005684886888891571, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3688}, {\"ngram\": \"her eyes\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic glory\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's welterweight quarterfinals\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite Khelif's dominant win over her Italian adversary, underdog Hamori remains unfazed.\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3873, \"end\": 3880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9893894773710225, \"rank\": 0.008657581281007258, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's dominant win\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"underdog Hamori\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She boldly stated to the press: \\\"I am not scared.\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 3975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the press\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not care about the press story and social media.\", \"from\": 3976, \"to\": 4029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the press story\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she or he is a man, it will be a bigger victory for me if I win.\\\"\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"a bigger victory\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, amid growing debates, Olympic champion Nicola Adamsraised concerns over fairness and safetyin women's competitions.\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"growing debates\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4127}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4145}, {\"ngram\": \"fairness and safetyin women's competitions\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time gold medallist expressed her views openly, saying: \\\"After years of fighting for women's boxing to even exist in the Olympics and then all the training they go through to get there it was hard to watch another fighter be forced to give up on her Olympic dreams.\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two-time gold medallist\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"her views\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4271}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"fighting\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4312}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4361}, {\"ngram\": \"another fighter\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4453}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic dreams\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"\\\"People not born as biological women, that have been through male puberty, should not be able to compete in women's sport.\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4507}, {\"ngram\": \"biological women\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4536}, {\"ngram\": \"male puberty\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4573}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only is this unfair it's dangerous!\\\"\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There promises to be significantly more discourse about Khelif the dee